Set the Correct CWD and APACHE and MIME_TYPES_LOC variables in TestFunc.pm
and you should be set to use all the .pl test programs.

Edit the httpd.template file and the x.pl file you want to use for testing.
Pay attention to the file locations, use the Unix notation for directories
even on Windows.

Directories should be created automatically for you in your Current
Working Directory. index.html in the server root and 0.html thru 24.html
are created in origins servers' directories.

Under Windows, make sure your firewall is set up correctly !

backuptest-rest.pl and backuptest-masteronly.pl are to be used under Windows,
while a equivalent test script backuptest.pl can be used under Unix.
